The National Working Committee, NWC of the All Progressives Congress, APC has expelled the Party executives in Zamfara State at all levels. Yekini Nabena, APC Acting National Publicity Secretary said, by this decision all supposed Party factions in Zamfara State stands dissolved. Nabena stated that, “NWC-inaugurated committee for Zamfara State are to conduct the Governorship and Legislative primaries in the State. Hence, the Zamfara State Governor, H.E. Alh. Abdul’aziz Abubakar Yari and the dissolved executives in the state should not interfere in the primary elections in the State”. He reaffirmed that, “the Governorship and legislative primaries will hold from Saturday, October 5, 2018 – Sunday, October 6, 2018”. 